parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Intermittent Brake Failure with Grinding Noise and ABS Activation
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose stopping power, leading to accidents or near-misses, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal goes to the floor
the brake light on the dashboard illuminates
and a grinding or pulsating noise is heard when applying the brakes.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake Light Illumination with Intermittent Brake Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose stopping power, leading to accidents or near-misses, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake light on the dashboard illuminates

and the vehicle may experience intermittent brake failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ECU can cause the vehicle to shut off suddenly, leading to loss of power, loss of brakes, and loss of steering, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
The failure of the airbag and seatbelt system can cause the airbag light to flash, and the seatbelts may not function properly in the event of an accident, which can lead to serious injury or death.
The failure of the IPDM can cause the vehicle to die while driving, leading to loss of power, loss of brakes, and loss of steering, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Climate Control and Electrical System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the climate control and electrical system can cause the air conditioner, turn signals, and speedometer to malfunction, which can lead to accidents or discomfort while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Cruise Control and Laser Guided System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cruise control and laser guided system can cause the instrument panel to malfunction, and the vehicle to suddenly stop running, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
The malfunction of the airbag system can lead to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash, potentially causing serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is on or blinking continuously
the airbag system may not function during a crash
the passenger airbag turns off intermittently
the airbag system may not deploy in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the seat belt pretensioner wiring can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash, potentially causing serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light comes on
the airbag system may not function during a crash
the seat belt pretensioner wiring is faulty.
